Package: SpatialMetabolics
Title: Spatial Metabolic Analysis for Visium HD Brain Transcriptomics
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Eric", "Prince", 
           email = "eric.prince@cuanschutz.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7359-6608"))
Description: Comprehensive toolkit for analyzing ATP regulation, mitochondrial 
    function, and metabolic states in spatial transcriptomics data. Optimized 
    for Visium HD brain tissue analysis with seamless Seurat integration.
    Provides specialized functions for metabolic pathway scoring, spatial 
    gradient detection, and publication-ready visualization.
